                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d590">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">861.77/2331a: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Ambassador in Japan</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Warren</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1921-11-29T18:00:00-05:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">November 29, 1921—6 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>205. Repeat following to Caldwell:<note n="47" xml:id="d590fn47">Consul John K.
                        Caldwell, on special duty at Chita.</note>
                    <quote rend="blockquote">
                        <p>Having regard to rumors that the Chita government threatens seizure of
                            the Chinese Eastern to prevent international control, you may intimate
                            to the appropriate authorities informally and unofficially that any
                            measures of international supervision or control which may be decided
                            upon will have for their purpose, as heretofore, a conservation of the
                            legal status of the railway and its ultimate return to those in interest
                            without an impairing of any existing rights.</p>
                    </quote>
                </p>
                <p>Repeat to Peking as Dept’s 309 for information.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hughes</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
